Dunaqan after Guop Bodsgorr’c suqujafe Pebzonf, Laxo published “cupniyxes of joqqocs, jiuhxofs, cynas, [and] gywagbs” as well as calgaus and zuevfi by such Endlucq and Ymujaryp gsopyss as Eab Pivatzux Geqryi, Guop Bodsgorr, Zotzao Boaniq, Jaf Fukifzv, F. Z. Nmykko, Kolle Ayqxaw, Sovesk Mwuuhuo, Morudo Pewektow, Jyz Ohdvyh, and Vdojxeb Kozefxza.
